-- Reliance Industries' Credit Risk Rises on Telecom Venture, Moody's Says
-- Dinakar Sethuraman
-- 2010-06-21T03:55:58Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-21/reliance-industries-credit-risk-rises-on-telecom-venture-moody-s-says.html

          
          
             Reliance Industries Ltd. has
increased its risk by diversifying into the telecommunications
business and acquiring a broadband provider for $1 billion,
Moody’s Investors Service said in a note today. The move carries
“negative credit” implications, it said.  
